    dc:title "Revision of Pseudocorinna Simon and a new related genus (Araneae: Corinnidae): two more examples of spider templates with a large range of complexity in the genitalia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440502>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440504>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440498>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440500>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440508>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440514> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440502>
    dc:description "Figure 45. Scanning electron micrography pictures of warts. Crinopseudoa billeni sp. nov., male paratype (MRAC 217478) (A, B), Crinopseudoa bong sp. nov., male paratype (MRAC 218174) (C, D), Crinopseudoa catharinae sp. nov., male paratype (MRAC 217423) (E, F), and Crinopseudoa flomoi sp. nov., female paratype (MRAC 217438) (G, H). A, C, E, G, warts in front of fovea; B, D, F, detail of previous; H, detail of carapace wart. Arrows indicate excretory pore." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440502/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440504>
    dc:description "Figure 46. Scanning electron micrography pictures. Crinopseudoa caligula sp. nov., female paratype (A) and male paratype (B, L) (both MRAC 216812), Crinopseudoa otus sp. nov., male paratype (C, F, G–I) (MRAC 216775), Crinopseudoa flomoi sp. nov., male paratype (D, K) (MRAC 217460) and female paratype (E) (MRAC 217438), and Crinopseudoa ephialtes sp. nov., male paratype (MRAC 218197) (J). A, wart in front of fovea; B, retrolateral trichobothrium on male palpal tibia; C, dorsal bothria at base of tarsus; D, seta on wart in front of fovea; E, preening brush on leg III; F, tarsal organ on leg II; G, chelicerae, frontal view; H, detail of previous; I, modified setae, detail of previous; J, left palpal tibia, retrolateral view; K, right palpal tibia, retrolateral view; L, retrolateral tibial apophysis, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440504/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440498>
    dc:description "Figure 43. Crinopseudoa bong sp. nov., female paratype (MRAC 216616) (A–C) and male paratype (MRAC 216616) (D, E). A, habitus, dorsal; B, habitus, ventral; C: mouthparts; D, habitus, dorsal; E, prosoma. Scale bars: A, B, D = 0.5 mm; C, E = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440498/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440500>
    dc:description "Figure 44. Crinopseudoa bong sp. nov., male holotype (MRAC 217745). A, carapace, dorsal view; B, carapace, lateral view; C, prosoma, ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440500/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440508>
    dc:description "Figure 47. Crinopseudoa bong sp. nov., female paratype (MRAC 216949) (A–C) and male paratype (MRAC 218174) (D–F). A, anterior lateral spinnerets (ALS); B, posterior median spinnerets (PMS); C, posterior lateral spinnerets (PLS); D, ALS; E, PMS; F, PLS. ac, aciniform gland spigot(s); cyl, cylindrical gland spigot(s); mAp, minor ampullate gland spigot(s); MAp, major ampullate gland spigot(s); p, piriform gland spigot(s); t, tartipore." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5440514>
    dc:description "Figure 49. Crinopseudoa bong sp. nov., male holotype (MRAC 216745) (A–C) and female paratype (MRAC 216775) (D, E). A, B, right male palp, retrolateral and ventral views; C, male palpal tibia, dorsal view; D, cleared epigyne, dorsal view; E, epigyne, ventral view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm. CAPT, central apophysis of posterior part of tegulum; E, embolus; FC, functional conductor; MA, median apophysis; PAPT, prolateral apophysis of posterior part of tegulum PTA, prolateral tibial apophysis; RTA, retrolateral tibial apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5440514/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

